snippet.title: Black Clover: Quartet Knights - Overview Trailer | PS4, PC
snippet.description:
Want to know more about Black Clover: Quartet Knights? We got your back. Check out this overview trailer for the upcoming game based on the hit anime series! 

Black Clover: Quartet Knights releases 9/14/18 for PS4 and PC.
